messages.text: What can I do on this site?
messages.author: user

messages.text:
I can help you find a job! I can also help you build your resume, practice for interviews, and get more training.

Are you currently a Medicaid member residing in Washington, D.C., Florida, Iowa, Kansas, Missouri, Nevada, or Ohio?
messages.author: ai

messages.text: Yes
messages.author: user

messages.text:
Great! RangamWorks is here to help you find a job.

Here are some of the things you can do on the site:

*   **Find a Job:** You can start your job search [here](https://rangamworks.com/JobSeeker/DirectorySearchJob?directory=home&utm_source=rangamworks&utm_medium=chatarbor&utm_campaign=job+search+question).
*   **Build Your Resume:** Log in, go to your Dashboard, Edit Profile, progress to the Review page, and click "Download Resume."
*   **Take a Job Interest Survey:** Log in, go to your Dashboard, find the "Surveys" card, and click the link next to "Job Interest."

How else can I help you today?

messages.text: How can you help me find a job?
messages.author: user

messages.text:
I can help you find a job on our site! Our platform specializes in connecting Medicaid members in Washington, D.C., Florida, Iowa, Kansas, Missouri, Nevada, and Ohio with meaningful employment opportunities.

To start your job search, you can visit our [Job Search page](https://rangamworks.com/JobSeeker/DirectorySearchJob?directory=home&utm_source=rangamworks&utm_medium=chatarbor&utm_campaign=job+search+question). You can also create a profile to help match you with jobs that fit your skills and interests!

Are you a Medicaid member in one of the listed states?
messages.author: ai

messages.text: Yep
messages.author: user

messages.text:
Great! I can point out some features to help you find a job!

*   **Job Search:** You can start your job search [here](https://rangamworks.com/JobSeeker/DirectorySearchJob?directory=home&utm_source=rangamworks&utm_medium=chatarbor&utm_campaign=job+search+question).
*   **Edit Profile:** To enter your job preferences, skills, and work history, log in, go to your Dashboard, and click "Finish filling out your profile..."
*   **Job Interest Survey:** After you log in, find the "Surveys" card on your Dashboard and click the link next to "Job Interest".

Would you like me to explain any of these in more detail?
messages.author: ai

messages.text: The survey
messages.author: user

messages.text:
The Job Interest survey helps us match you with the right jobs. To find it, log in, go to your Dashboard, find the "Surveys" card, and click the link next to "Job Interest." Completing this survey will improve your job recommendations.

Would you like me to walk you through any other features?

messages.text: How does RangamWorks help job seekers?
messages.author: user

messages.text:
RangamWorks helps you find jobs and gives you tools to succeed.

Here's how we help:
*   We help you find many types of jobs.
*   We match you with jobs based on your skills and interests.
*   We offer training to help you learn new skills.

Ready to explore? You can start your job search [here](https://rangamworks.com/JobSeeker/DirectorySearchJob?directory=home&utm_source=rangamworks&utm_medium=chatarbor&utm_campaign=job+search+question)!

messages.text: Do I need an email address?
messages.author: user

messages.text:
Yes, you'll need an email address to sign up for RangamWorks.

If you think your current email looks unprofessional, I can help! Our [Professional Email Address Course](https://learn.rangamworks.com/mod/resource/view.php?id=13) can help you set up a clean, job-ready email in minutes. It will help you look professional to employers and keep your applications organized!

Are you a Medicaid member in Washington, D.C., Florida, Iowa, Kansas, Missouri, Nevada, or Ohio?
messages.author: ai

messages.text: I'm looking for project manager roles in Chicago.
messages.author: user

messages.text:
I can help you search for jobs. However, I can only assist Medicaid members in Washington, D.C., Florida, Iowa, Kansas, Missouri, Nevada, and Ohio.

I am unable to search for jobs outside of those states. Are you a Medicaid member in one of those states?
messages.author: ai

messages.text: Yes, Iowa. How about project manager roles in Iowa?
messages.author: user

messages.text:
Great! I can help you find project manager roles in Iowa.

You can start your search on our [Job Search page](https://rangamworks.com/JobSeeker/DirectorySearchJob?directory=home&utm_source=rangamworks&utm_medium=chatarbor&utm_campaign=job+search+question). You can filter by job title and location to find relevant opportunities.

While you're at it, have you completed the Job Interest Survey? You can find it on your Dashboard in the "Surveys" card. Click the "[X]% Completed" link next to "Job Interest". It will help us match you with jobs that fit your interests!
